azizex666:  Another heartfelt Thank You for your Christmas presents that you give all of us complete strangers- that I am sure is the fruit of countless hours of work for you- just to make a bunch of strangers extremely happy. You are like Robin Hood. I am disabled and on an extremely fixed income that does not leave me enough disposable cash to buy even one bestseller, and reading books on my e-reader is one of the very few things that keep me sane. I know the publishers would probably string you up if they could- but you are not doing them the dis-service they think you are. I do write reviews on the bestsellers and send out only to friends and immediate friends of friends- and only upon their request to be added to my listserv. The list is just a little over 200, and between them- and those that they forward to or pass on by work of mouth. So if there are any publishers reading this- there is some positive here for you as well. Thanks AZIZEX666!
